584
00:28:00,039 --> 00:28:00,759
Seriously.

585
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:05,519
We're off, boss.

586
00:28:05,519 --> 00:28:06,279
We're off, boss.

587
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:10,039
Those people ahead of them...

588
00:28:10,079 --> 00:28:11,359
Don't forget to log that list.

589
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:39,759
Where did everyone go?

590
00:28:40,240 --> 00:28:40,920
