591
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:41,640
Run!

592
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:42,640
Go!

593
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:43,920
Police! Don't move!

594
00:28:45,039 --> 00:28:45,759
