599
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:00,119
Li Na.

600
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,200
Who the hell is this guy?

601
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:05,799
He hits so hard.

602
00:29:06,319 --> 00:29:06,880
Right?

603
00:29:08,359 --> 00:29:10,640
This guy shares a room with you every day.

604
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:11,759
And you say you don't know him?

605
00:29:13,279 --> 00:29:14,440
Shares a room with me?

606
00:29:16,799 --> 00:29:18,000
