610
00:29:23,200 --> 00:29:24,279
Let me introduce you.

611
00:29:24,759 --> 00:29:27,279
Cheng Liang, five armed robberies.

612
00:29:27,359 --> 00:29:28,400
Phones, computers, cash.

613
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:29,400
He also injured three people.

614
00:29:29,599 --> 00:29:30,279
It's him.

615
