622
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:48,279
No money.

623
00:29:48,279 --> 00:29:49,160
No money.

624
00:29:51,519 --> 00:29:52,799
Does pocket money count?

625
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:54,960
Just for food and drinks and stuff.

626
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:56,160
If we wanted something,

627
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:57,559
