628
00:29:57,680 --> 00:29:59,319
He would buy it for us directly.

629
00:30:00,119 --> 00:30:01,680
We didn't really need any money.

630
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:03,279
That Tao,

631
00:30:03,279 --> 00:30:05,200
whatever he told you to do, you did it?

632
00:30:05,559 --> 00:30:07,319
Whoever he told you to rob, you robbed?

633
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,920
Tao treated us so well.

634
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:10,960
He took care of our food and housing.

635
00:30:11,279 --> 00:30:12,240
So helping him out with some robberies

636
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,599
