639
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,000
You're only nineteen and already doing this.

640
00:30:19,039 --> 00:30:20,000
Who told you to do it?

641
00:30:21,279 --> 00:30:22,160
No one told me to.

642
00:30:22,359 --> 00:30:23,079
I did it willingly.

643
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:27,119
What's your relationship with Chen Tao? Tell me.

644
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:32,400
Stop asking, I won't tell you.

645
00:30:33,599 --> 00:30:34,400
My dad died.

646
00:30:36,359 --> 00:30:37,160
How did he die?

647
00:30:37,839 --> 00:30:38,559
Brain cancer.

648
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:40,920
He was gone in just a month.

649
00:30:41,599 --> 00:30:43,319
What about your mom? Doesn't she take care of you?

650
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,640
I don't need her to.

651
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:47,319
It'd be better if she never cared about me at all.

652
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:49,880
What did she do to you?

653
00:30:50,519 --> 00:30:51,640
As soon as my dad was hospitalized,

654
00:30:53,039 --> 00:30:54,640
