655
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,480
How did you meet Chen Tao?

656
00:31:00,119 --> 00:31:01,119
Na-jie introduced us.

657
00:31:02,279 --> 00:31:03,759
How did you meet Li Na?

658
00:31:04,039 --> 00:31:05,000
We met at an internet café.

659
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,119
Na-jie is like a goddess to me.

660
00:31:07,839 --> 00:31:09,720
When I get married, I want someone like Na-jie.

661
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,400
Li Na introduced you to Chen Tao,

662
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:12,480
and you just went along with him?

663
00:31:12,519 --> 00:31:13,319
Yeah.

664
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:15,440
Tao-ge treats me really well.

665
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:17,160
He spoils me more than my dad ever did.

666
00:31:17,279 --> 00:31:18,480
How does he treat you so well?

667
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:20,680
He celebrates my birthday.

668
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:23,160
Buys me phones and computers.

669
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:24,920
Basically, everything I have

670
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,200
was bought by Tao-ge.

671
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:29,759
I remember once when I had a fever,

672
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:32,279
he tucked me into bed

673
00:31:32,480 --> 00:31:33,920
and stayed with me the whole night.

674
00:31:34,519 --> 00:31:36,599
Things my parents never did for me in their whole lives,

675
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,079
he did them all for me.

676
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:41,880
Brother

677
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:44,240
Did you guys arrest Tao too?

678
00:31:46,839 --> 00:31:47,880
Can you let him go?

679
00:31:48,599 --> 00:31:49,759
He's really a good person.

680
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,960
Everything was done by us.

681
00:31:53,240 --> 00:31:54,359
It has nothing to do with him.

682
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:56,480
He didn't—he didn't force me either.

683
00:31:57,559 --> 00:31:58,240
Really.

684
00:31:58,880 --> 00:32:00,720
But the others have already confessed.

685
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:01,799
They said

686
00:32:03,319 --> 00:32:04,440
you were the one who ordered it.

687
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:07,519
I ordered it?

688
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:12,920
That's what they just said, right?

689
00:32:13,119 --> 00:32:14,160
He did it all.

690
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:17,880
I just felt sorry for them.

691
00:32:18,079 --> 00:32:19,039
Wanted to make friends.

692
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:21,640
I just gave them a place to stay.

693
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:24,839
How could they turn on me like this?

694
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,880
Isn't this just like

695
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:28,960
the story of the farmer and the snake?

696
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:30,599
Even though the face isn't clear,

697
00:32:30,599 --> 00:32:31,279
but from the car,

698
00:32:31,279 --> 00:32:32,039
Brother Dali,

699
00:32:32,799 --> 00:32:34,799
