700
00:32:35,279 --> 00:32:35,599
Tell me.

701
00:32:35,599 --> 00:32:36,079
Look.

702
00:32:37,119 --> 00:32:38,720
Chen Tao was convicted of theft the year before last

703
00:32:38,759 --> 00:32:39,640
and sentenced to eighteen months.

704
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:41,000
He was only released at the end of last year.

705
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:42,440
His girlfriend isn't simple either.

706
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:44,119
Li Na, a few years ago,

707
00:32:44,119 --> 00:32:45,119
was arrested during an anti-vice operation.

708
00:32:45,119 --> 00:32:46,000
Now she's out.

709
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:47,640
She has recruited more than twenty women under her.

710
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:49,720
They use this chat app to commit online fraud.

711
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:51,680
Let's go meet Li Na.

712
00:32:58,559 --> 00:33:01,359
Taozi's situation has nothing to do with me.

713
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:02,960
I don't know anything.

714
00:33:04,319 --> 00:33:05,000
Alright.

715
00:33:05,559 --> 00:33:07,759
Then let's talk about your own situation.

716
00:33:08,519 --> 00:33:09,799
What situation do I have?

717
00:33:10,079 --> 00:33:11,559
Chen Tao treats you well.

718
00:33:11,759 --> 00:33:13,759
Your outfit isn't cheap, is it?

719
00:33:14,279 --> 00:33:15,480
He bought all of it for you.

720
00:33:15,759 --> 00:33:17,480
I bought these clothes myself.

721
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:19,519
Really?

722
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,359
So what do you do for work?

723
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:24,000
How much do you make a month?

724
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:37,440
There are over two hundred people in the QQ group.

725
00:33:38,119 --> 00:33:39,160
There are three groups in total.

726
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,759
You must type a lot every day, right?

727
00:33:41,759 --> 00:33:43,200
I didn't send that.

728
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:46,920
Even if I did send it,

729
00:33:47,119 --> 00:33:48,640
