730
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:02,519
If you think I'm guilty, then sentence me.

731
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:05,759
Anyway, I don't know anything about Taozi.

732
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:08,800
You're really protecting Chen Tao.

733
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:11,639
I think you're someone who values relationships.

734
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:14,199
But while you protect him,

735
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:15,639
