736
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:18,559
I don't know if he protects me or not.

737
00:34:19,039 --> 00:34:20,320
He's pretty good to me.

738
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:22,079
If he truly cared about you,

739
00:34:22,639 --> 00:34:24,079
he wouldn't have let you get involved.

740
00:34:24,079 --> 00:34:25,400
Renting these two apartments.

741
00:34:25,519 --> 00:34:26,760
