743
00:34:28,199 --> 00:34:29,760
You're providing a place

744
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:30,880
for a robbery gang to commit crimes.

745
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:33,000
Do you really not understand this yourself?

746
00:34:39,159 --> 00:34:39,679
Brother Li

747
00:34:39,679 --> 00:34:40,599
Big Brother Li

748
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:42,400
Look at that expression.

749
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:43,800
He hasn't opened his mouth.

750
00:34:44,239 --> 00:34:45,079
If you have something to say, just say it.

751
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:46,440
I have a lead here.

752
00:34:47,119 --> 00:34:49,760
Li Na has a subordinate named Liu Liping.

753
00:34:49,760 --> 00:34:51,039
She used to be a hostess too.

754
00:34:51,039 --> 00:34:52,280
The two of them were very close.

755
00:34:52,559 --> 00:34:53,519
But because of this Chen Tao,

756
00:34:53,519 --> 00:34:55,199
he bought Liu Liping a phone.

757
00:34:55,239 --> 00:34:56,360
The two of them fell out.

758
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,840
They still don't talk to each other.

759
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:59,679
This is Liu Liping's statement.

760
00:35:00,719 --> 00:35:01,920
You found this lead?

761
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:02,679
I found it.

762
00:35:02,719 --> 00:35:03,920
I helped him find it.

763
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:07,000
I knew it, with your brain...

764
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,119
Alright, continue questioning Li Na.

765
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:17,679
Or should we let her cool off for a bit first?

766
00:35:18,719 --> 00:35:19,519
Why?

767
00:35:19,719 --> 00:35:20,519
I think...

768
00:35:20,519 --> 00:35:22,599
The interval between the two interrogations is too short.

769
00:35:22,599 --> 00:35:23,679
It might not be effective.

770
00:35:23,960 --> 00:35:24,679
That's true.

771
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:25,679
Alright.

772
00:35:25,679 --> 00:35:26,679
Then let's let her cool off for now.

773
00:35:26,679 --> 00:35:27,559
We'll talk to her after she's cooled off.

774
00:35:27,559 --> 00:35:28,039
Okay.

775
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,039
Thanks for your hard work.

776
00:35:29,039 --> 00:35:30,119
It's nothing, just doing my job.

777
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,840
I think you're right.

778
00:35:37,519 --> 00:35:38,880
There will be cake later.

779
00:35:41,719 --> 00:35:42,360
The cake you ordered.

780
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:43,079
Thank you.

781
00:35:44,239 --> 00:35:44,719
Don't eat it.

782
00:35:44,719 --> 00:35:45,159
You're welcome.

783
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:45,920
Okay.

784
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:48,519
