785
00:35:48,519 --> 00:35:49,840
I heard you're still coughing.

786
00:35:50,159 --> 00:35:51,400
I'm almost recovered.

787
00:35:51,599 --> 00:35:55,840
Can we go inside and play for a while?

788
00:36:00,639 --> 00:36:02,320
Where have you been lately?

789
00:36:03,039 --> 00:36:04,639
I don't believe you went abroad.

790
00:36:06,159 --> 00:36:07,360
I didn't go abroad.

791
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,760
I was hiding out in a hotel.

792
00:36:14,719 --> 00:36:18,360
I just wanted some time alone.

793
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:19,239
To really think things over.

794
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:21,079
I've figured things out.

795
00:36:21,079 --> 00:36:22,400
And I've made my decision.

796
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:24,840
What's your decision?

797
00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:28,519
Sis, let me ask you.

798
00:36:29,639 --> 00:36:30,840
Do you love Li Wei?

799
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:37,280
I... actually,

800
00:36:38,679 --> 00:36:40,320
When I first got together with Ziming,

801
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:42,400
I didn't even know what it meant to love someone.

802
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:44,559
I didn't know if I loved him.

803
00:36:44,920 --> 00:36:46,760
But after a few months together,

804
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:49,760
One of his colleagues, Lao Ma, passed away.

805
00:36:50,599 --> 00:36:51,920
He went to the funeral.

806
00:36:52,239 --> 00:36:53,760
When he came back, he broke up with me.

807
00:36:54,519 --> 00:36:57,199
I knew he was doing it for my sake.

808
00:36:58,280 --> 00:36:59,760
From that moment on,

809
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:02,960
I truly, deeply loved him.

810
00:37:04,039 --> 00:37:06,039
So when did those feelings start to fade?

811
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:12,599
Feelings like that don't just disappear all at once.

812
00:37:13,199 --> 00:37:15,800
So many things have happened over the years.

813
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:16,400
It's just...

814
00:37:17,079 --> 00:37:20,159
They slowly faded away, little by little.

815
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:25,840
Was it because of the last surgery?

816
00:37:29,000 --> 00:37:30,360
That's one of the reasons.

817
00:37:37,199 --> 00:37:38,800
I hope you'll think it over again.

818
00:37:43,960 --> 00:37:45,480
Think more about the child, too.

819
00:37:49,719 --> 00:37:50,280
Mm.

820
00:37:51,639 --> 00:37:52,960
I don't want to eat.

821
00:37:53,559 --> 00:37:55,119
If you don't want to eat, then don't.

822
00:37:56,840 --> 00:38:00,360
Sis, can we still be friends in the future?

823
00:38:07,719 --> 00:38:09,840
We checked Chen Tao's bank transfer records.

824
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:12,079
Several transfers were made to someone

825
00:38:12,079 --> 00:38:13,679
named Liu Liping.

826
00:38:14,599 --> 00:38:16,800
Who is Liu Liping? Do you know her?

827
00:38:18,559 --> 00:38:20,280
I knew something was going on between them.

828
00:38:21,119 --> 00:38:22,159
He also said

829
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,199
most of the money is with you.

830
00:38:24,239 --> 00:38:25,039
Where did you put it?

831
00:38:25,039 --> 00:38:25,760
Nonsense.

832
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,800
He never gave me a single cent.

833
00:38:28,079 --> 00:38:30,079
Even if a meal is a bit expensive, we have to split it evenly.

834
00:38:30,639 --> 00:38:32,679
Liu Liping said you've been with Chen Tao for four or five years.

835
00:38:32,679 --> 00:38:33,760
But he still won't marry you.

836
00:38:34,519 --> 00:38:35,880
Is it because you have a child?

837
00:38:36,039 --> 00:38:37,320
Liu Liping doesn't have a child.

838
00:38:37,920 --> 00:38:39,119
What do you mean?

839
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:41,880
Your son should be starting elementary school in September, right?

840
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:44,519
He's living with his grandparents in the northeast.

841
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:45,880
It's not easy, is it?

842
00:38:47,239 --> 00:38:48,719
Does he know what you do?

843
00:38:49,599 --> 00:38:50,719
What do I do?

844
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,119
